Description_lang: Each stack of Thrash reduces the target's damage to you by $s3% and increases your damage to them by $s1%.

description_blz.en_US: Each stack of Thrash reduces the target's damage to you by 2% and increases your damage to them by 2%.
description_blz.es_MX: Cada acumulación de Vapulear reduce un 2% el daño del objetivo en tu contra y aumenta un 2% el daño que le infliges.
description_blz.pt_BR: Cada aplicação de Surra reduz em 2% o dano que o alvo causa a você e aumenta em 2% o dano que você causa a ele.
description_blz.de_DE: Jeder Stapel 'Hauen' verringert Euren durch das Ziel erlittenen Schaden um 2% und erhöht Euren verursachten Schaden gegen dieses Ziel um 2%.
description_blz.en_GB: Each stack of Thrash reduces the target's damage to you by 2% and increases your damage to them by 2%.
description_blz.es_ES: Cada acumulación de Vapulear reduce un 2% el daño que recibes del objetivo y aumenta un 2% el daño que le infliges.
description_blz.fr_FR: Chaque charge de la technique Rosser réduit les dégâts que la cible vous inflige de 2% et augmente ceux que vous lui faites subir de 2%.
description_blz.it_IT: Ogni accumulo di Falciata riduce i danni a te inflitti dal bersaglio del 2% e aumenta i danni da te inflitti al bersaglio del 2%.
description_blz.ru_RU: Каждый эффект "Взбучки" увеличивает урон, который вы наносите цели, на 2%, и уменьшает урон, получаемый вами от цели, на 2%.
description_blz.ko_KR: 난타 중첩당 대상으로부터 받는 피해는 2%만큼 감소하고 대상에 대한 자신의 공격력은 2%만큼 증가합니다.
description_blz.zh_TW: 每堆疊一層痛擊，可使目標對你造成的傷害降低2%，並使你對其造成的傷害提高2%。
description_blz.zh_CN: 每一层痛击都会使目标对你造成的伤害降低2%，而你对目标造成的伤害提高2%。
